Name: Inspector_FlexPropertiesCategoryTT
English: These properties will only affect children which are also flex panels
Translation: 这些属性只会影响也是 flex 布局的子元素。

Name: Flex_AlignContent_TT
English: Align content defines the distribution of lines along the cross-axis. This only has effect when items are wrapped to multiple lines using flex wrap.
Translation: 对齐内容(Align content)定义了沿横轴的线条分布。这仅在项目使用 flex 换行时有效。

Name: Flex_MarginPaddingFmt
column6: margin and padding label w/ colour formatting

Name: Flex_TT_RuntimeDraw
English: How the UI layer is drawn at runtime, defining its boundaries, relative position and anchoring
Translation: 如何在运行时绘制UI层，定义其边界，相对位置和锚定

Name: Flex_TT_Width
English: Specifies the width of the node's border box
Translation: 指定节点的边界框的宽度

Name: Flex_TT_Height
English: Specifies the height of the node's border box
Translation: 指定节点的边界框的高度

Name: Flex_TT_AlignItems
English: Align children along the cross axis of their container
Translation: 将子元素沿其容器的交叉轴对齐

Name: Flex_TT_JustifyContent
English: Align children along the flex panel node’s main axis (Flex Direction)
Translation: 沿 flex panel 节点的主轴对子元素进行对齐(Flex Direction)

Name: Flex_TT_Padding
English: Spacing between node’s inner edge and children
Translation: 节点的内边缘和子节点之间的间距

Name: Flex_TT_Margin
English: Spacing around the outside of the node

Name: Flex_TT_FlexDirection
English: The main axis or direction nodes are laid out. This influences the direction of other flex properties e.g. align items, flex wrap.
Translation: 主轴或方向节点已布局。这会影响其他flex属性的方向，例如对齐项目、flex换行。

Name: Flex_TT_LayoutDirection
English: Layout direction of the node and its children
Translation: 节点及其子节点的布局方向

Name: Flex_TT_Wrap
English: Move items to the next row/column when it exceeds flex panel dimensions
Translation: 当超过flex布局尺度时，将项目移动到下一行/列。

Name: Flex_TT_Position
English: Distance between the edges of the node and its parent
Translation: 节点边缘与其父节点之间的距离

Name: Flex_TT_AlignSelf
English: Align node along the cross axis of its container
Translation: 使节点沿其容器的交叉轴对齐。

Name: Flex_TT_ClipContent
Translation: 隐藏超出面板边界的项目

Name: Flex_TT_Grow
English: Describes how remaining space in the container node should be distributed among its children along the main axis
Translation: 描述容器节点中的剩余空间应如何沿主轴在其子节点之间分配

Name: Flex_TT_Shrink
English: Describes how to shrink children along the main axis in the case that the total size of the children overflow the size of the container on the main axis
Translation: 描述如何在子元素的总大小超过主轴上容器的大小的情况下，沿主轴缩小子元素

Name: Flex_TT_Display
English: Include or remove from the layout

Name: Flex_TT_Anchor
English: Sets the item’s 0,0 position based on its container
Translation: 根据其容器设置项目的 0,0 位置。

Name: Flex_TT_Visible
English: Hide item from rendering at startup. Any attached scripts are not deactivated
Translation: 在启动时隐藏项目不渲染。任何附加的脚本都不会被停用

Name: Flex_TT_Stretch
English: Stretch to fit the container’s width or height
Translation: 自动适应容器的宽度或高度

Name: Flex_TT_TileHori
English: Repeat across X axis inside container
Translation: 在容器内沿 X 轴重复

Name: Flex_TT_TileVert
English: Repeat across Y axis inside container
Translation: 在容器内沿 Y 轴重复

Name: Flex_TT_KeepAspect
English: Preserves aspect ratio when the item is stretched
Translation: 拉伸项目时保持纵横比

Name: Help_eYGPositionType_YGPositionTypeStatic
English: Behaves like relative except it will ignore position offsets
Translation: 行为上类似于相对(relative)，但会忽略位置偏移量。

Name: Help_eYGPositionType_YGPositionTypeRelative
English: Laid out according to the flow of the flex container it is part of
Translation: 根据其所属的flex容器的流程进行布局

Name: Help_eYGPositionType_YGPositionTypeAbsolute
English: Absolute nodes do not take up space in its flex container
Translation: 绝对定位(Absolute)节点不会占用其flex容器中的空间

Name: Help_eYGDisplay_YGDisplayFlex
English: Laid out according to the flex algorithm

Name: Help_eYGDisplay_YGDisplayNone
English: Removed from the layout tree and will not be visible
Translation: 从布局树中移除，将不再可见

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignFlexStart
English: Align wrapped lines to cross axis’s start
Translation: 将换行内容对齐到交叉轴的起始位置

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignFlexEnd
English: Align wrapped lines to cross axis’s end
Translation: 将换行内容对齐到交叉轴的末端位置

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignCenter
English: Align wrapped lines to cross axis’s centre
Translation: 将换行内容对齐到交叉轴的中心位置

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignSpaceBetween
English: Distribute wrapped lines evenly across the main axis with remaining container space
Translation: 在主轴方向上均匀分布换行内容，并利用容器剩余空间

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignSpaceAround
English: Distribute wrapped lines evenly with remaining container space, with half that size between first and last line
Translation: 在主轴方向上均匀分布换行内容并利用剩余空间，且首行与末行之间的间距为该剩余空间的一半

Name: Help_alignContent_YGAlignSpaceEvenly
English: Distribute wrapped lines evenly with remaining container space, including start and end edges
Translation: 在主轴方向上均匀分布换行内容并利用剩余空间，包括起始边和结束边

Name: Help_eYGUnit_YGUnitPoint
English: Defines the width/height in absolute pixels
Translation: 定义宽度/高度为绝对像素值

Name: Help_eYGUnit_YGUnitPercent
English: Defines the width/height as a percentage of its containing block's size
Translation: 定义宽度/高度为其包含块大小的百分比

Name: Help_eYGUnit_YGUnitAuto
English: Calculates the width/height for the node based on its content
Translation: 根据节点内容自动计算其宽度/高度

Name: Help_eYGFlexDirection_YGFlexDirectionColumn
English: Align children from top to bottom

Name: Help_eYGFlexDirection_YGFlexDirectionColumnReverse
English: Align children from bottom to top

Name: Help_eYGFlexDirection_YGFlexDirectionRow
English: Align children from left to right

Name: Help_eYGFlexDirection_YGFlexDirectionRowReverse
English: Align children from right to left

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifyFlexStart
English: Align children to main axis’s start
Translation: 将子元素对齐到主轴起始位置

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifyCenter
English: Align children to main axis’s centre
Translation: 将子元素对齐到主轴中心位置

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifyFlexEnd
English: Align children to main axis’s end
Translation: 将子元素对齐到主轴末端位置

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifySpaceBetween
English: Distribute children evenly across the main axis with remaining container space
Translation: 在主轴上均匀分布子元素，并使用剩余容器空间。

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifySpaceAround
English: Distribute children evenly with remaining container space, with half that size between first and last child
Translation: 将子元素均匀分布在剩余容器空间中，在第一个和最后一个子元素之间留出一半大小的间距。

Name: Help_eYGJustify_YGJustifySpaceEvenly
English: Distribute children evenly with remaining container space, including start and end edges
Translation: 将子元素均匀分布在剩余容器空间中，包括起始和结束边缘

Name: ggs_signing_id_tooltip
English:
To distribute your title outside of the Mac App Store macOS requires that your
package is codesigned. Please provide the signing identity that you wish to use
here: this should be a Developer ID Application identity and should be present
in your Mac's login keychain certificates. Signing identities can be easily created
in Xcode->Preferences->Accounts->Team->View Details->Developer ID
Application->Create. Signing identities will be matched so the default value
should be sufficient if you are only the member of one development team.
Translation:
要在 Mac App Store 之外分发您的标题，macOS 要求您的软件包已进行代码签名。请在此处提供您想使用的签名身份：
这应该是一个 Developer ID Application 身份，并且应存在于您 Mac 的登录钥匙串证书中。
签名身份可以轻松地在 Xcode->Preferences->Accounts->Team->View Details->Developer ID
Application->Create 中创建。系统会匹配签名身份，因此如果您仅属于一个开发团队，默认值就足够了。

On Mac - /Users/Shared/GameMakerStudio2
On PC - C:\ProgramData\GameMakerStudio2

On Mac-/Users/Shared/GameMakerStudio2
On PC-C:\ProgramData\GameMakerStudio2

Important
By pressing Send, you are providing consent for us to process the data detailed below in line with our Privacy Policy.
Translation:
我们已经创建了错误报告，以便我们可以检查和防止此类问题。如果您可以提供该次出错的详细背景信息，将有非常大的帮助具体而言，就是您之前正在进行的操作。

 重要 
 按发送"即表示您同意我们根据我们的隐私政策来处理您提交的内容"

If you have any concerns about our use of data, please email our data controller at datacontroller@yoyogames.com Form version:

Translation: GM2041 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_push_state()。

Name: Feather_GM2042
English: GM2042 - Inconsistent stack depth for gpu_push_state()/gpu_pop_state() blocks. All branches should call these functions an equal number of times.
Translation: GM2042 - gpu_push_state()/gpu_pop_state() 块的堆栈深度不一致。所有分支都应调用这些函数相同的次数。

Name: Feather_GM2043
English: GM2043 - Attempting to access the local variable '{0}' outside of the scope it was defined in.
Translation: GM2043 - 试图访问定义范围之外的局部变量 '{0}' 。

Name: Feather_GM2044
English: GM2044 - Local variable '{0}' is already declared.

Name: Feather_GM2045
English: GM2045 - Local variable '{0}' is unset before reading it.
Translation: GM2045 - 局部变量 '{0}' 在读取之前未设置。

Name: Feather_GM2046
English: GM2046 - Inconsistent stack depth for surface_set_target()/surface_reset_target() blocks. All branches should call these functions the same number of times.
Translation: GM2046 - surface_set_target()/surface_reset_target() 块的堆栈深度不一致。所有分支都应该以相同的次数调用这些函数。

Name: Feather_GM2048
English: GM2048 - Not all code paths call gpu_set_blendenable(true) before the end of the script.
Translation: GM2048 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_blendenable(true)。

Name: Feather_GM2049
English: GM2049 - Not all code paths call gpu_set_zfunc(cmpfunc_lessequal) before the end of the script.
Translation: GM2049 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_zfunc(cmpfunc_lessequal)。

Name: Feather_GM2050

Name: Feather_GM2051

Translation: GM2051 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_cullmode(cull_noculling)。

Name: Feather_GM2053

Translation: GM2053 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_alphatestenable(false)。

Name: Feather_GM2054

Translation: GM2054 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_alphatestref(0)。

Name: Feather_GM2055

Translation: GM2055 - 并非所有代码都在脚本结束前调用 gpu_set_texfilter(false)。

Translation: GM2059 - 试图释放已经释放的资源。

Translation: GM2061 - 使用nullish运算符的时机。

Name: BugReport_Overall
English: Thanks for submitting your issues. Before you send this report, please do see How to submit a Bug Report.
Translation: 感谢您提交问题。在发送此报告之前，请参阅如何提交Bug报告。

Name: BugReport_KnownIssues
English: Please check the Known Issues before submitting to make sure that it has not already been reported.
Translation: 请在提交之前检查 已知问题 以确保尚未报告该问题。

Name: BugReport_SecurityIssues
English: If you believe you have found a security vulnerability, please report the issue here
Translation: 如果您认为您发现了一个安全漏洞，请在此处报告此问题这里。

Name: BugReport_AuthGithub
English: You can authorise your GitHub account to post issues on the Accounts page
Translation: 您可以授权您的 GitHub 帐户在帐户页面上发布问题

Name: BugReport_DescriptionText
English: Describe the issue in as much detail as possible, the more details you supply, the more likely we are able to fix the problem. Include details such as: what you were doing at the time, and target platforms being used.
Translation: 尽可能详细地描述问题，您提供的细节越多，我们就越有可能解决问题。包括一些细节，比如: 你当时在做什么，以及正在使用的目标平台。

Name: BugReport_DescriptionText_Prefab
English: Describe the issue in as much detail as possible - please be aware only official GameMaker prefabs are supported for this bug type. If your issue happens with any other prefab, please use the correct "Project Fails To Build" or "In-Game form instead!""
Translation: 请尽可能详细地描述问题，请注意，只有官方的GameMaker预制件才支持这种错误类型。如果您的问题在使用其他 预制件 时发生，请使用正确的"项目构建失败"或"游戏内"表单！

Name: BugReport_DescriptionText_Extension
English: Describe the issue in as much detail as possible - please be aware only official GameMaker extensions are supported for this bug type. If your issue happens with any other extension, please use the correct "Project Fails To Build" or "In-Game" form instead!
Translation: "请尽可能详细地描述问题，请注意，只有官方的GameMaker扩展程序才能处理此类型的错误。如果您的问题在使用任何其他扩展程序时发生，请使用正确的"项目构建失败"或"游戏内"表单！

Name: BugReport_DescWarning
English: Please complete the fields marked * to submit
Translation: 请填写标有 * 的字段以提交

Name: BugReport_TitleMinCharWarning
English: Title should have at least {0} characters

Name: BugReport_DescMinCharWarning
English: Description should have at least {0} characters
Translation: 描述应至少包含{0}个字符

Name: BugReport_Steps_ProjectTool
English: Steps To Reproduce (note that you should also use the file-selector below to attach a .zip containing your entire project folder)
Translation: 重现步骤（请使用下方的文件选择器附加包含整个项目文件夹的 .zip 文件）
Comment: project tool cat repro steps text

Name: BugReport_StepsTT
English: Describe the steps required to reproduce the bug
Translation: 描述复现错误所需的步骤

Name: BugReport_AttachHeader
English: Would you like to privately attach:

Name: BugReport_AttachFilesTT
English: Your GameMaker logs are already included automatically, as they are essential to diagnose the issue. Here you can attach screenshots and in-game logs, etc., to give additional information.
Translation: 您的 GameMaker 日志已经自动包含，因为它们对于诊断问题至关重要。您可以在此处附加截图和游戏内日志等，以提供更多信息。

Name: BugReport_IncludeProjectTT
English: Please allow GameMaker to send us a project that shows the issue - ideally, a small sample rather than your full game, as we want to identify the fix as soon as possible. Reports found to be coding mistakes/development support may be closed without detailed explanations.
Translation: 请允许GameMaker发送一个项目给我们，展示该问题——理想情况下，提供一个小型的示例而非您的完整游戏，因为我们希望尽快找到修复方案。发现的问题如果被判定为编码错误或开发支持请求，可能会在没有详细解释的情况下关闭。

Name: BugeReport_IssueVisTT
English: Note that this affects the visibility of your bug report text only. All attachments above are always only visible to GameMaker staff.
Translation: 请注意，这仅影响您的错误报告文本的可见性。 上述所有附件始终仅对 GameMaker 工作人员可见。

Name: BugReport_IncludePrefabs
Comment: Include a copy of the used prefabs within the project

Name: BugReport_IncludePrefabsTT
English: Include a copy of all Prefab Collections that are used within this Project. This should be done if you use custom Prefabs that are not publicly available.
Translation: 包含项目中使用的所有预制件集。如果使用不可公开获取的自定义预制件，则应执行此操作。
Comment: Tooltip explaining that Prefabs need to be copied into the Project if there is no public access to them

Name: BugRep_ReqProj_Message
English:
Would you like to include the current project in your bug report?

A project is typically required to diagnose compiling or in-game issues.

If you do not include a sample project we may request one later if we cannot reproduce the issue.
Translation:
您想将当前项目包含在您的错误报告中吗？

项目通常需要诊断编译或游戏内问题。

如果我们无法重现该问题，且当您不包括示例项目施，我们可能会在稍后请求示例项目。

Name: BugRep_ReqProj_TT_Yes
English: Include current project and send the report
Translation: 包括当前项目并发送报告

Name: BugRep_ReqProj_TT_No
English: Send the report without including the project
Translation: 发送不包括项目的报告

Name: BugRep_ReqProj_TT_Cancel
English: Return to the bug report form

Name: BugRep_IncludeCrashProject
English:
The project '{0}' was open when the issue occurred.

Would you like to privately include this project with your report?

Including the project will improve the chances of the issue being resolved.
Translation:
项目 '{0}' 在问题发生时处于打开状态。

您是否希望将此项目私密包含在您的报告中？

包含该项目将提高问题得到解决的可能性。

Name: BugRep_ReqPrefabs_Title
Comment: Include all prefabs in the project

Name: BugRep_ReqPrefabs_Message
English:
Would you like to include the current project's prefabs in your bug report?

A project is typically required to diagnose compiling or in-game issues.

If you do not also include the prefabs and they are not publicly accessible, we may request them later if we cannot reproduce the issue.
Translation:
您是否希望在您的错误报告中包含当前项目的预制件？

通常需要项目来诊断编译或游戏中的问题。
